name: Rick's Auto Collision
overview: When your vehicle enters the repair facility at Rick’s Auto Collision, you can rest assured that you have left your car in the hands of true professionals. Our I-CAR trained and ASE certified technicians, utilizing their extensive training, experience, and craftsmanship, not only make your vehicle look as good as it did before the accident, but by utilizing the most technologically advanced equipment at their disposal, including our Genesis 2 computerized structural scanning system, our technicians know that your vehicle is back to its original factory specifications. Our technicians also know that your vehicle is as safe and structurally sound as it was before the accident.
